                    <span>This book along with other books from many different people helped my get through tough times easier.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A great Introduction</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
